    "summary": "This section enables retrieval for questions concerning annual market revenue and growth trends from 2021 to 2025. It specifically answers:\n- **Topics & Entities:** Market revenue scale and year-over-year growth rates.\n- **Dates:** Annual data points for 2021, 2022, 2023, 2024, and 2025.\n- **Metrics:** Exact revenue figures (in billion RMB) and percentage growth rates for each listed year.\n- **Claims/Trends:** Identification of years with positive growth (2021, 2023, 2025) versus negative growth/contraction (2022, 2024).\n- **Evidence Type:** Quantitative financial/market data presented as a structured numerical list.\n- **Definitions, Procedures, Tables, Figures:** Not present; the section contains only raw annual metrics without explanatory definitions, procedural steps, or embedded visual tables/figures."
