    "summary": "This section provides the legend and contextual description for a figure analyzing US mobile game market revenue concentration. It supports retrieval for questions regarding:\n- **Figure Interpretation & Definitions:** What do the visual elements represent? (Blue bars = US mobile game market revenue scale in 100M RMB; Cyan line = growth rate %).\n- **Data Segmentation:** How is market revenue distributed by game ranking? (Categorized into Top 1-10, 11-50, 51-200, and Others, represented by blue, cyan, green, and orange respectively).\n- **Dates & Timeframe:** Which years are compared in the analysis? (2023, 2024, and 2025).\n- **Metrics:** What quantitative measures are tracked? (Revenue scale in 亿元 RMB, year-over-year growth rate %, and revenue concentration/share percentages by ranking tier).\n- **Evidence & Source:** Who produced the data and visualization? (点点数据 independent research and drawing).\n- **Topic & Claim:** What market trend is being analyzed? (2025 US mobile game market revenue concentration and its distribution shifts across ranking brackets over a three-year period)."
